data.description: There is space galore in this Greystone home located on a corner lot! The main level features an abundance of living space and functional flow. Upon entry, you will be welcomed to a living room that is open to the eat-in kitchen. The kitchen also opens to a cozy family room with fireplace. The additional flex space on the 1st level has multiple possibilities as a bedroom, work, or play space. Upstairs, there's even more living space with the spacious loft. The primary suite hosts an en suite w/double vanity, garden tub, and huge walk in closet! There are an additional 3 bedrooms upstairs along with a hall bath. Updates include a freshly painted interior, vinyl plank flooring throughout, new water heater, and 5 year old HVAC. Additional photos to come, but don't miss this one!
